NG0189:1: nub phyogs mkha' 'gro mnyen gsal sud ka'i gdong *//
NG0189:2: phyag drug dang po pad+ma b+han+d+har ldan //
NG0189:3: bar ma gnyis na zhags pa tri shul bsnams //
NG0189:4: tha ma'i phyag gis ce spyang zhing chung bsnyod //
NG0189:5: byang phyogs mkha' 'gro khyung gdong yang gsal g.yos //
NG0189:6: phyag drug dang po rgya gram b+han+d+ha bsnams //
NG0189:7: bar ma gnyis na dbyug tho rgyu phreng 'dzin //
NG0189:8: tha ma'i phyag gis spyang ki zhing chung bsnyod //
NG0189:9: nam mkha'i mkha' 'gro bkrag gsal rdo rje'i mchu //
NG0189:10: phyag drug dang po 'khor lo b+han+dar ldan //
NG0189:11: bar ma gnyis na rgyal mtshan spu gri 'dzin //
NG0189:12: tha ma gnyis kyi 'ug pa zhing chung bsnyod //
NG0189:13: dbyings kyi yum chen rtag pa'i rgyal mo lnga //
NG0189:14: dbu gsum zhabs bzhi rang rigs sku mdog gsal //
NG0189:15: srid pa bde 'gro dbu gsum sku mdog mthing *//
NG0189:16: phyag drug dang po 'khor lo rin po che //
NG0189:17: bar ma g.yang gzhi b+han+da dmar gyis bkang *//
NG0189:18: tha ma gnyis ni tshe bum lcags kyu 'dzin //
NG0189:19: nyi zla thod phreng mdog dkar 'ja' 'od gsal //
NG0189:20: phyag gnyis zangs lcags snying phraing zhags pa 'phen //
NG0189:21: nyi ma khros ma mdog dkar spu gri 'dzin /
NG0189:22: khrag 'thung khros ma sngon mo thod khrag 'dzin //
NG0189:23: bdud rtsi khros ma dmar mo bum pa bsnams //
NG0189:24: bde sbyor khros ma ljang nag ti ra 'phyar //
NG0189:25: srid pa'i rgyan byed dkar mo skra zhags 'dzin //
NG0189:26: sngon mo dbyings phyug zhing gi dbyug pa thogs //
NG0189:27: bdag nyid dmar mo rgyu ma'i zhags pa 'phen //
NG0189:28: gcig spyod ser mo zhing lpags g.yang gzhi brdebs //
NG0189:29: dkar mo mig gcig b+han+d+ha zlum po thogs //
NG0189:30: nag mo mche gtsigs b+han+d+ha ser po thogs //
NG0189:31: dmar mo dbang sdud b+han+d+ha lcang lo 'phyang *//
NG0189:32: ser mo las mkhan thod pa rgya gram thogs //
NG0189:33: srid pa chags byed mthing nag mi snying bsnams //
NG0189:34: srid pa cha snyoms dmar mo thod khrag 'dzin //
NG0189:35: 'dod khams gtso mo sngon mo khram shing bsnams //
NG0189:36: ral gcig dmar mo kha t+wam mi ro 'dzin //
NG0189:37: gling bzhi spyi phud dkar gsal lcags kyu thogs //
NG0189:38: rin chen srid 'degs sngon mo ga'u 'dzin //
NG0189:39: pad+ma gar dbang le brgan thod khrag thogs //
NG0189:40: rdo rje gar dbang ser mo b+han+da 'dzin //
NG0189:41: har ting dkar mo me yi dkyil 'khor thogs //
NG0189:42: dun ting nag mo yi dkyil 'khor thogs //
NG0189:43: shan+ting dmar mo chu yi dkyil 'khor thogs //
NG0189:44: grub ting ser mo klung gi dkyil 'khor thogs //
NG0189:45: srin mo skam mo dkar mo shel phur thogs //
NG0189:46: srin mo phor thogs sngon mo thod khrag 'dzin //
NG0189:47: srin mo g.yang gzhi thod sbram b+han+d+ha 'dzin //
NG0189:48: srin mo za ba dmar mo zhing lpags brdebs //
NG0189:49: srin mo gsod byed ser mo lcags kyu thogs //
NG0189:50: srin mo dmar ser thod phrag zhags pa 'dzin //
NG0189:51: srin mo snom byed sngon mo lcang lo 'phyar //
NG0189:52: dkar mo mche gtsigs thod pa dkar po thogs //
NG0189:55: dmar mo mchu 'jibs b+han+d+ha dmar mo thogs //
NG0189:56: ser mo las mkhan b+han+da ser po 'dzin //
NG0189:57: lha yi sring mo dkar mo rdo rje bsnams //
NG0189:58: gshin rje'i sring mo sngon mo thod dbyug thogs //
NG0189:59: klu yi sring mo dmar mo sbrul zhags thogs //
NG0189:60: gnod sbyin sring mo ser nag ne'u le 'dzin //
NG0189:61: bde bar gshegs pa rbod gtong 'dus pa'i bdag / rang rig phyag rgya'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NG0189:62: nub byang dkyil 'khor 'jig rten dregs pa'i gtso //
NG0189:63: bcom ldan dpal chen dregs pa kun 'dul ni //
NG0189:64: dbug gsum phyag drug kham nag smug mthing zhal //
NG0189:65: dang po'i phyag gnyis rdo rje dung khrag dkrugs //
NG0189:66: g.yas g.yon phyag bzhis lha brgyad klu brgyad mgo khams gsum spyi 'dul phyag g.yas rdo rje 'khyud //
NG0189:67: phyag g.yon dung khrag gtso bo'i zhal du stob //
NG0189:68: lha chen mthing nag gri gug tsit+ta g.yon //
NG0189:69: btsun mo u ma rtse gsum thod khrag bsnams //
NG0189:70: seng ge glang chen gshibs pa'i khri la bzhugs //
NG0189:71: ya ma ra dza mdog nag be con g.yas //
NG0189:72: g.yon na thod dbyug ma he chu glang bcibs //
NG0189:73: sgrol byed nag mo srid pa'i 'khor lo bskor //
NG0189:74: bdud po skos rje mthing nag khram shing g.yas //
NG0189:75: g.yon na dgra s+t+wa bdud rta nag po bcibs //
NG0189:76: nag mo re ti khram shing nad rkyal bsnams //
NG0189:77: drel rta dmar mo rkang gsum chibs su bcibs //
NG0189:78: nag po glog phreng glog gi phreng ba 'dzin //
NG0189:79: sbal mgo khrag mig khrag phor zhal du 'dzin //
NG0189:80: yab yum gnyis med 'brug dang rnga mo bcibs //
NG0189:81: yak+sha me dbal mthing nag rin chen bsnams //
NG0189:82: g.yon na mtshon thogs stag seng rngam pa bcibs //
NG0189:83: mon mo nag mo phyag g.yas spu gri bsnams //
NG0189:84: g.yon na spyang ki'i lcags kyi phag mo bcibs //
NG0189:85: srid pa'i rgyal mo mdog dkar 'khor lo g.yas //
NG0189:86: g.yon na me long 'brug mo sgra chen bcibs //
NG0189:87: e ka tsa ti smug mthing tsit+ta g.yas // g.yon na g.yu spyang dre'u rta nag po bcibs //
NG0189:88: nag mo mgyogs byed g.yas na mtshon drub bsnams //
NG0189:89: g.yon na nad rkyal so bya nag po bcibs //
NG0189:90: rdo rje bdud 'dul mthing nag khrag thun g.yas //
NG0189:91: g.yon na mdung thung dre'u rta nag po bcibs //
NG0189:92: srog zan dmar po bse mdung dmar po g.yas //
NG0189:93: g.yon na mda' gzhu chibs su rta dmar bcibs //
NG0189:94: skyes bu dmar 'bar shang lang g.yas na bsnams //
NG0189:95: g.yon na zangs zhags chibs su rta dmar bcibs //
NG0189:96: bgegs kyi rgyal po mthing nag kha t+wam g.yas //
NG0189:97: g.yon na thod khrag chibs su rta nag bcibs //
NG0189:98: ka la nag po phyag g.yas rtse gsum bsnams //
NG0189:99: g.yon na thod khrag chibs su rtsal chen bcibs //
NG0189:100: dmu bdud nag po g.yas na shang langs bsnams //
NG0189:101: g.yon na mda' gzhu dmu rta mchong rgod bcibs //
NG0189:102: gang ba bzang po dkar po ba dan @#//
NG0189:104: g.yon na shel gyi gnam ru dkar po bcibs //
NG0189:105: spyi bdud rgyal po mdog dkar ru mtshon g.yas //
NG0189:106: g.yon na ral gri rdo rta gro bo bcibs //
NG0189:107: gnam mthil dkar po g.yas na dar dkar bsnams //
NG0189:108: g.yon na ral gri chibs su rta dkar bcibs //
NG0189:109: tshangs pa dkar po g.yas na nyi zer bsnams //
NG0189:110: g.yon pa spu gri seng ge dkar mo bcibs //
NG0189:111: rdo rje chung rgyal dkar po bdud zhags g.yas //
NG0189:112: g.yon na spu gri ba glang sna ring bcibs //
NG0189:113: skyes bu sku lha mdog dkar rdo rje g.yas //
NG0189:114: g.yon na ru mtshon tsa ra khams pa bcibs //
NG0189:115: legs ldan nag po gri gug g.yas na bsnams //
NG0189:116: g.yon na beng chen bdud rta nag po bcibs //
NG0189:117: gza' bdud rgyal po mdog nag sku smad sbrul //
NG0189:118: phyag g.yas mda' gzhu g.yon na sbrul zhags bsnams //
NG0189:119: thog gi bu yug dmar skya thog ser 'phen //
NG0189:120: yab yum gnyis med 'brug chen yid mgyogs bcibs //
NG0189:121: klu mdud nag po sbrul zhags nad rkyal bsnams //
NG0189:122: sku smad sbrul gyi chu srin sngon po bcibs //
NG0189:123: yak+sha nag mo nad rkyal dug thun bsnams //
NG0189:124: sku smad sbrul 'khyil rus sbal nag po mnan //
NG0189:125: 'jig rten las byed dreg pa can gyi tshogs //
NG0189:126: rang rig phyag rgya'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NG0189:127: byang shar dkyil 'khor drag sngags lha yi tshogs //
NG0189:128: bcom ldan dpal chen stobs ldan nag po ni //
NG0189:129: dbu gsum phyag drug mthing nag drag po'i zhal //
NG0189:130: phyag drug dang po rdo rje dung khrag dkrugs //
NG0189:131: 'og ma'i phyag bzhis lha klu tsit+ta bsnams //
NG0189:132: 'byung lnga'i bdag mo zhal gcig sku mdog mthing *//
NG0189:133: g.yas g.yon phyag gis mkha' 'degs sa gzhi mnan //
NG0189:134: 'chi bdag mthing nag thod pa gri gug bsnams //
NG0189:135: btsun mo nag mo gtso chen yab kyi tshul //
NG0189:136: bdud mo nag po kha rlangs tri shul g.yas //
NG0189:137: nag mo khrag 'dzag khram bam thod rlon bsnams //
NG0189:138: gsod byed nag po ral gri thod khrag g.yon //
NG0189:139: sring mo nag mo gri gug mi mgo bsnams //
NG0189:140: gnod sbyin sngo nag ral gri ru mtshon bsnams //
NG0189:141: ral gcig sngon mo zhing lpags dar nag bsnams //
NG0189:142: lha chen dkar po b+han+d+ha shel gri bsnams //
NG0189:143: thar pa nag pau mchod gtor mthun gtor bsnams //
NG0189:144: rje btsan nag po dar nag zhags pa bsnams //
NG0189:145: yak+sha nag po kha t+wam gri gug bsnams //
NG0189:146: har mdzes dkar po shel gri dar dkar bsnams //
NG0189:147: yam shud dmar po mdung dmar ral gri bsnams //
NG0189:148: rdo rje mdzes pa dmar po ru mtshon 'phyar //
NG0189:149: pho nya lag dgu mdog ser sprul pa 'gyed /
NG0189:150: khyab 'jug nag po khram shing dgra s+t+wa bsnams //
NG0189:151: gzhon nu gtum po bum pa rus sbal 'dzin //
NG0189:152: sngags kyi bdag po dregs pa bco brgyad rnams //
NG0189:153: kun kyang zhing lpags rlon pa'i na bza' gsol //
NG0189:154: zhabs gnyis dgra dang bgegs kyi snying la gzer //
NG0189:155: dmod pa'i mtshon chang lha yi tshogs @#//
NG0189:157: rang rig phyag rgya'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NG0189:158: lho nub dkyil 'khor rig pa 'dzin pa'i tshogs //
NG0189:159: grub pa chen po brgyad la dbang bsgyur zhing *//
NG0189:160: mthun 'jug theg pa rab ston byang chub sems //
NG0189:161: phyag rgya che dang lhun gyis grub pa dang *//
NG0189:162: rnam par smin dang tshe la dbang ba dang *//
NG0189:163: man ngag lung ston shes rab rgyun spel zhing */
NG0189:164: dam tshig dbang bskur nyams pa bskang mdzad pa'i //
NG0189:165: rgyal tshab rig 'dzin byang chub sems dpa' rnams //
NG0189:166: rang rig phyag rgya'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NG0189:167: 'di dag rang gi phyag rgya ste //
NG0189:168: dang po mchod pa chen po yis //
NG0189:169: gnyis pa rab tu bstod pa ste //
NG0189:170: yon tan rtags bcas tshig gis mnyes //
NG0189:171: gsum pa 'dod pa'i yon tan tshogs //
NG0189:172: gzugs sgra dri ro reg chos so //
NG0189:173: bzhi pa nyon mongs lnga nyid de //
NG0189:174: lnga pa sgrol ba skye 'chi med //
NG0189:175: drug pa 'bral med sbyor ba ste //
NG0189:176: bdun pa dug gsum phung pos mchod //
NG0189:177: brgyad pa dug lnga sman yin te //
NG0189:178: dgu pa rmad byung mchod pa che //
NG0189:179: bcu pa dam tshig bdud rtsi'o //
NG0189:180: bcu gcig pa ni zhal zas tshogs //
NG0189:181: bcu gnyis gtsang sbyor lhag ma ste //
NG0189:182: 'di dag gis ni nga dang bcas //
NG0189:183: dus gsum rgyal ba kun mnyes 'gyur //
NG0189:184: de yis bsgrub par bya ba dag / kun gyi mthar phyir yon tan tshogs //
NG0189:185: ma lus skyed byed 'di yin no //
NG0189:186: kye ma dpal ldan he ru ka / dpal chen nga yi dgongs chen po //
NG0189:187: rigs brgyad dgu yis rab mdzes pa'i //
NG0189:188: rten 'gyur gcig gis sgrub pa la //
NG0189:189: sku gsung thugs dang yon tan dang *//
NG0189:190: phrin las rbod gtong sgrub mchod dang *//
NG0189:191: dmod pa drag shul bstan bya rnams //
NG0189:192: zhi rgyud rig pa 'dzin dang bcas //
NG0189:193: zhi dang khro dang thun mong bcas //
NG0189:194: pho nya las ky-i byed pa dag / nga yis bshad pa gang yin pa //
NG0189:195: ma 'ongs dus na brtse ldan pa'i //
NG0189:196: byang chub sems dpa' grags chen po //
NG0189:197: phyi dang nang dang sbas dang gsang *//
NG0189:198: thun mong khyad par bye brag rnams //
NG0189:199: gang gis bsngags pa rnams la ston //
NG0189:201: bde bar gshegs pa thams cad 'dus pa'i rgyud rab tu 'byed pa las /
NG0189:202: lha nges par dbyung zhing bsgrub pa'i le'u ste drug
NG0189:203: pa'o // // de nas he ru ka rigs lnga
NG0189:204: la sogs pa'i 'khor rnams kyis bcom ldan 'das la
NG0189:206: kye ma bcom ldan 'das kun tu bzang po khyod
NG0189:207: kyi sku dang gsung dang thugs dang yon tan dang
NG0189:208: phrin las kyi khyad par dang */
NG0189:209: rbod gtong dang pho nya dang dmod pa la sogs
NG0189:210: pa khro bo khro mo drag shul spyod pa'i las
NG0189:211: / nges par bzung ba 'di dag bstan pa dang bshad pa dang brjod pa'i yul ni gang */
NG0189:212: dus ni ji tsam zhig na lags /
NG0189:214: yon tan ni ci zhig yod pa lags /
NG0189:215: bdag cag gi the tshom bcad du gsol //
NG0189:219: kye ma he ru ka yi tshogs //
NG0189:220: 'khor dang bcas pa kun nyon cig / phyi ma'i dus na nga yi sku //
NG0189:221: sprul pa thun mong snang ba 'di /
NG0189:222: chos sku mnyam pa nyid gyur tshe //
NG0189:223: thos pa dang ni rig pa 'dzin //
NG0189:224: skyes bu rnams kyi yid la gnas //
NG0189:225: rin chen dgu yi sprul pa'i gzugs //
NG0189:226: 'jam dbyangs lha dang bcas pa yis //
NG0189:227: legs bkod nam mkha'i cho 'phrul ston //
NG0189:228: kun tu bzang pos nyer snang zhing *//
NG0189:229: 'jig rten dregs pa'i tshogs bcas kyis //
NG0189:230: dpal ldan mkha' 'gro'i gnas dag tu //
NG0189:231: gsang ba'i rgya yis btab byas pa //
NG0189:232: lo ni brgya dang nyi shu nas //
NG0189:233: kun bzang dgongs pa skong byed pa //
NG0189:234: rig pa 'dzin pa rnams la snang *//
NG0189:235: yan lag phyogs bcur rgyas par byed //
NG0189:236: rdo rje gsang ba'i myu gu yis /
NG0189:237: khyad par bsam gyis mi khyab pa //
NG0189:238: gdul bar bya ba rnams la ston //
NG0189:240: de yi gtso gyur 'jig rten mgon //
NG0189:241: shwa ra b+ha gi lha yi bu //
NG0189:242: rnam sprul bkod pa mchod dag gis //
NG0189:243: byang chub sems dpa' rig pa 'dzin //
NG0189:244: dbang bsgyur yongs rdzogs der 'byung gis /
NG0189:245: khyod rnams bshung bar ma byed cig / ces bka'
NG0189:246: stsal nas bcom ldan 'das he ru ka yum dang
NG0189:247: gnyis su med pa sku'i zhing bkod pa dang bcas
NG0189:248: pa chos kyi dbyings su thim par gyur to //
NG0189:249: 'khor 'jig rten gyi dregs pa can rnams kyang bcom
NG0189:250: ldan 'das nyid kyi gsung rjes su bsgrub cing thugs
NG0189:251: zhi ba chos kyi skur mthong bar gyur nas //
NG0189:252: bcom ldan 'das la rjes su yi rang zhing mngon par bstod do //
NG0189:253: bde bar gshegs pa thams cad 'dus pa'i rgyud rab tu 'byed pa las /
NG0189:254: phyi ma nges par 'byung ba bstan pa'i le'u ste bdun pa'o ///
NG0189:255: / khro bo chen po mngon par rdzogs par sangs
NG0189:256: rgyas pa'i yid bzhin gy-i yon tan chen po nges
NG0189:257: par bstan pa'i skabs te gnyis pa rdzogs so //
NG0189:258: // bde bar gshegs pa thams cad 'dus pa'i rgyud
NG0189:259: rab tu 'byed pa'i lde mig lta bur bshad pa
NG0189:260: rdzogs so // // zhi ba la le'u bcu /
NG0189:261: khro bo la bdun te bcu bdun yod pa /
NG0189:262: rgya gar gyi mkhan po slob dpon chen po pad+ma 'byung gnas dang */
NG0189:263: bod kyi lo ts+tsha ba bai ro tsa nas bsgyur cing zhus te gtan la phab pa'o //
